{"tid":1699660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 報仇","createTime":"2019-11-08T06:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T07:55:32.000Z","uid":31205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfe8d5f215a1bd00894ac9768f123d8b3eb463a","tid":1699660,"uid":31205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:07:05.000Z","msg":"五個月了 我地得到左啲咩? 撤回?<br />\n615梁烈士以死明志 大家話: 佢唔係跳落黎 佢係比暴政推落黎<br />\n我地失去一個又一個手足 每一條活生生既人命 死喺極權政府同警暴既手下<br />\n但係 我地絕對唔可以對手足既犧牲麻木 絕對唔可以對黑警既暴力常態化<br />\n我地必須要行動升級去反抗 我地必須為每一個犧牲既手足報仇 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推翻呢個暴政 清算所有黑警</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人 肯罷工未? 人地命都無埋啦! 仲掛住你果份兩萬蚊既人工呀? 求下大家 必須參與全面無限期三罷</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港人 報仇</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>血債 血償</strong></span></span><br />\n最後 <br />\n希望所有犧牲既手足能夠尋冤得雪<br />\n淨低既我地 煲底見"},{"pid":"60e583f5657473a8e3c15ab97902a2a13a7d570e","tid":1699660,"uid":50561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:08:00.000Z","msg":"害死人個對狗男女 認住佢地"},{"pid":"1b87abe7e0ee1dbc8e0d2f94a8a810d9f4874973","tid":1699660,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"願周烈士安息  我們必定血債血償《告香港人書》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1699563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1699563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區願周烈士安息  我們必定血債血償《告香港人書》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1699563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1699563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"187291c31b9ae3a32735e548bd8f64b7e6661404","tid":1699660,"uid":31205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"呢對賤畜必不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=